data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath home located on almost a half an acre located at the corner of Emjay and Thornton. Yard is fenced and has a rolling gate at the driveway. Nice workshop behind a carport and a second storage building. Roof was re-shingled in 2021. Separate RV hookups on the property. Kitchen is open to the living room. There is a separate office area off the living room. Nice north facing AZ room with mountain views. No HOA.
